@host={{HOST}}        // пример: http://localhost:8080
@clubId={{CLUB_ID}}   // пример: 42

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Check-in (valid QR, X-Telegram-Init-Data required)
POST {{host}}/api/clubs/{{clubId}}/checkin/scan
Content-Type: application/json
X-Telegram-Init-Data: {{INIT_DATA}}

{
  "qr": "{{QR_TOKEN}}"
}

### Preflight (CORS sanity)
OPTIONS {{host}}/api/clubs/{{clubId}}/checkin/scan
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: X-Telegram-Init-Data, Content-Type
Origin: https://t.me
